The '''Pestage family''' was the family of [[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]]. Residing in the [[Ciutric Hegemony]], they numbered over one hundred. When [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Delak Krennel]] seized control of the Hegemony from Pestage after murdering him, his next move was to coldly round up and execute all of Pestage's family members. None survived.

